{
  "stem": "8072.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they told you, you know, you're going to be there for awhile and then from there they're gonna send you to different labor camps or different-- not labor camps, like different housings and things like that.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't tell you you're gonna go to Auschwitz or Birkenau or something like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they're gonna resettle you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know for why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were happy where we were, but they were gonna resettle you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, you see shootings and beatings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Shootings, everything.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, this-- it was just a daily-- daily-- daily fact of life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in Krakow ghetto because this wasn't from my hometown.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know, but--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then came March 14, and I was sent to Auschwitz-- actually, Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Into Birkenau we went in open trucks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and again, we were loaded in that truck that you couldn't breath.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, just-- in fact, sometimes when they were taking the curve, around the curve I thought we were gonna all fall over and just keel over.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But somehow we made it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When we got to Birkenau, that-- that's was already all SS.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they came to the trucks and they used to say to get off the truck.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some people would say, you stay on the truck, and you get off the truck.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You stay on the truck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I noticed the people that they said to get off the truck was more the stronger, more the young-- not the-- not the older-- the younger one.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The-- the-- they ask him to get off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Me?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They told me to stay on the truck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when the guy turn-- turned, I jumped off the truck, you know, and I went with the other one.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
